Add `functools.wraps` decorator to the inner function wrapper in the decorator implementation: 
```
from functools import wraps
def platform_required(function):
    @wraps(function)
    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
        return function(*args, **kwargs)
    return wrapper
```
It will set original function docs to the wrapper.

